<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ de líng jù jí wǒ men xiāng jù zài shèng shān shàng,
 zhǔ de ài lián jié wǒ men chōng mǎn shén de róng guāng,
 zhǔ cì xià tiān shàng de ma nǎ qīn zì bǎ wǒ men wèi yǎng,
 wǒ men de xīn zhōng duō me xǐ lè, zàn měi zhǔ tóng huān chàng,
 zhǔ de huà shì jiǎo qián de dēng, yǒng bù mí shī fāng xiàng,
 zhǔ de huà shì lù shàng de guāng, yuè zǒu yuè yǒu lì liàng,
 zhǔ de huà shì shēng mìng zhī liáng, bù pà yǒu jī huāng,
 zhǔ de huà shì zhǔn shéng, yī shēng wèi wǒ dǎo háng.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ de líng jù jí wǒ men 迦南1371</title>
<hymn_number>1371</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>